== Configuration ==

=== Files ===

HexChat stores user specific configuration files in the {{Path|~/.config/hexchat/}} directory.

Settings can be modified graphically via the {{Path|Settings}} tab or using the {{c|/set}} command from the command-line interface.

=== SSL ===

In HexChat, enable SSL connections in {{Path|Network List}} ({{Key|Ctrl}}+{{Key|S}}){{Path| > Freenode > Edit}}. 

=== Auto-reconnect ===

In order to automatically reconnect after sleep/hibernate mode, enter the {{C|/set net_ping_timeout 31}} command.

